snippet.title: WrestleQuest - Official Developer Gameplay Walkthrough | Guerrilla Collective 2023 Showcase
snippet.description:
Join a member of the development team at Mega Cat Studios for a look at gameplay in this latest video for WrestleQuest, including a new area, enemies, and more from this upcoming game where pro wrestling and RPG fantasy collide. In WrestleQuest, “Macho Man” Randy Savage and tons of other icons guide your way to glory beyond the ring.

#GameTrailers #SoG #Gaming
